{"tid":977370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《哈利波特》終極二次創作　「霍格華茲祈禱和神跡學校」","createTime":"2019-01-11T06:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-11T06:56:22.000Z","uid":47714,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9e242cb822d3af8e397ed2206750dbbfe52c6f40","tid":977370,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:42:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/horrible.faith/photos/a.1613466505545958/2699848943574370/?type=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhorrible.faith%2Fphotos%2Fa.1613466505545958%2F2699848943574370%2F%3Ftype%3D3&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=f5114a23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/horrible.faith/photos/a.1613466505545958/2699848943574370/?type=3</a><br />\n<br />\n《哈利波特》的終極二次創作<br />\n<br />\n英國女孩欲閱讀《哈利波特》小說，其保守基督徒母親 Grace Ann 恐怕女兒看過小說後會變成女巫，便開始把小說重寫成「基督徒與無神論者」的鬥爭，將哈利波特送他去「霍格華茲祈禱和神跡學校」，鄧不利多成為了傳教士，以此對女兒自少灌輸對無神論者的仇恨。<br />\n<br />\nGrace Ann 認為這樣的修改是作為一位「基督教母親的職責」。<br />\n<br />\n參考：<a href=\"http://www.holyblasphemy.net/jesus-harry-potter-orthodox-icon-controversy-rocks-houston/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.holyblasphemy.net%2Fjesus-harry-potter-orthodox-icon-controversy-rocks-houston%2F&d=9wyTkkYHe0N7GaLerPJJfACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=90e4a675\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.holyblasphemy.net/jesus-harry-potter-orthodox-icon-controversy-rocks-houston/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://goo.gl/f9GjXq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Ff9GjXq&h=f0ff3589&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3d7c65ca3787ed992183fd87e655468d9d6debd8","tid":977370,"uid":53773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:42:49.000Z","msg":"哈神！"},{"pid":"85390aad1a8f56023a894a923ae06606822e9884","tid":977370,"uid":125168,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T06:44:09.000Z","msg":"無呢d由細到大嘅洗腦根本無正常嘅現代人會再信宗教"},{"pid":